{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019-06-01-primitive_reference/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"박준우 블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cad31ea3-0677-5c90-ae59-b89af840974b","excerpt":"원시값 Boolean Number String Null Undefined 참조값 Object 위의 예제들처럼 원시값은 value를 넘겨주고, 참조값은 변수의 값이 저장된 힙(Heap) 메모리의 주소값을 저장합니다. 다시한번 예제를 보겠습니다. 변수 a는 초기화시 Heap…","html":"<h1>\n    Primitive vs Reference\n</h1>\n<p>원시값</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Boolean</li>\n<li>Number</li>\n<li>String</li>\n<li>Null</li>\n<li>Undefined</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 원시 타입 변수 복사</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x\nx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">99</span>\ny <span class=\"token comment\">// 100</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>참조값</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Object</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 참조 타입 변수 복사</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> count<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x\nx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">99</span>\ny<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>count <span class=\"token comment\">//99</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 예제들처럼 원시값은 value를 넘겨주고, 참조값은 변수의 값이 저장된 힙(Heap) 메모리의 주소값을 저장합니다.</p>\n<p>다시한번 예제를 보겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"junwoo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  message<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> a\nb<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>message <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"good night\"</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//{</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//    name : \"junwoo\",</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//    message : \"good night\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//}</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//{</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//    name : \"junwoo\",</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//    message : \"good night\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>변수 a는 초기화시 Heap 메모리에 생성된 객체의 메모리 주소를 저장합니다.</p>\n<p>그리고 var b = a에서, 변수 a 초기화시 생성된 객체를 변수b에 복사하는게 아니라, a가 가진 메모리 주소, 즉 그 객체를 가리키는 메모리 주소를 복사하는 것입니다.</p>\n<p>따라서 변수 a와 b는 둘다 같은 메모리 위치를 가리키게 됩니다.</p>\n<p>같은 객체를 가리키는 것이므로, 변수a에 적용되는 변화는 변수b에게도 적용되게됩니다.</p>\n<p>아래의 예시처럼 함수에 argument를 넘겨줄 때에도 헷갈릴 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\n  b<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"hello world\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">500</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"good day\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 500</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"hello world\"</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"원시값, 참조값","date":"June 01, 2019","description":"원시값과 참조값 제대로 이해하고 넘어가기"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-05-27-git_reflog/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"git reflog로 hard-reset되돌리기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-06-01-ES6/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ES6 문법 공부"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"cad31ea3-0677-5c90-ae59-b89af840974b","previousPostId":"8d6ac114-f613-54f5-9634-4983c69da771","nextPostId":"b344afa1-4a9d-51c4-bddc-6671fb9ade05"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}